{"tid":357704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N件小學趣事","createTime":"2017-08-13T06:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T14:39:48.000Z","uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac74fa755f712ba4a98114db8841f73cad459565","tid":357704,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T06:50:41.000Z","msg":"之前開咗個post講幼稚園趣事,<br />\n今次想聽吓巴絲們小學嘅嘢.<br />\n上回:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/348926/page/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/348926/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n拋磚:<br />\n小一嗰陣有個同學成日擺拆開咗包裝嘅嘢食入櫃桶,<br />\n搞到惹咗好多蟻,<br />\nmiss話咗佢好多次都唔聽,<br />\n結果有日miss嬲得濟成張枱搬走咗唔比佢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外補充多個幼稚園嘅事:<br />\n有次未夠鐘放學,<br />\nmiss叫我哋圍住坐,<br />\n搵個同學仔出去是但唱首歌,<br />\n我都唔記得我係自己走出去定係比miss點中,<br />\n總之就出咗去唱.<br />\n你老味我諗起都想搵窿捐,<br />\n我居然挑戰盧巧音嗰隻好心分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知當時個miss有咩感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ea4dcdb4e0a17b36330184f42d8003b883b7b2","tid":357704,"uid":125322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:10:16.000Z","msg":"有次有個同學塞左舊擦膠入個鼻度，攞唔返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，搞到要入廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2c74aef9e2d25c1a8778a654f8a5f03b6c1542","tid":357704,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前開咗個post講幼稚園趣事,<br />\n今次想聽吓巴絲們小學嘅嘢.<br />\n上回:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/348926/page/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/348926/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n拋磚:<br />\n小一嗰陣有個同學成日擺拆開咗包裝嘅嘢食入櫃桶,<br />\n搞到惹咗好多蟻,<br />\nmiss話咗佢好多次都唔聽,<br />\n結果有日miss嬲得濟成張枱搬走咗唔比佢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外補充多個幼稚園嘅事:<br />\n有次未夠鐘放學,<br />\nmiss叫我哋圍住坐,<br />\n搵個同學仔出去是但唱首歌,<br />\n我都唔記得我係自己走出去定係比miss點中,<br />\n總之就出咗去唱.<br />\n你老味我諗起都想搵窿捐,<br />\n我居然挑戰盧巧音嗰隻好心分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知當時個miss有咩感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主今年應該都係最少19歲左右...幼稚園唱2002年先出既好心分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc9d022f99b622454efa481b81e924868e8b54d","tid":357704,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:46:04.000Z","msg":"我嗰陣小四，班上面成日有個男仔叻過我，咁嗰陣就考完英文派卷，我97 分，老師話最高分係陳大文同學(嗰個男仔)，有98分。我就勁唔開心，因為爭一分就可以攞英文全班第一(有得上台攞獎狀)。點知老師突然補返句: 但係因為陳大文同學佢係考試期間出左走廊玩，仲要整到警鐘誤鳴，所以要扣佢兩分！於是我就變左最高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b0aabb624a17fc46f708351bf6d6eca0d51a78","tid":357704,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我嗰陣小四，班上面成日有個男仔叻過我，咁嗰陣就考完英文派卷，我97 分，老師話最高分係陳大文同學(嗰個男仔)，有98分。我就勁唔開心，因為爭一分就可以攞英文全班第一(有得上台攞獎狀)。點知老師突然補返句: 但係因為陳大文同學佢係考試期間出左走廊玩，仲要整到警鐘誤鳴，所以要扣佢兩分！於是我就變左最高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/big