blockquote>小二同隔離位<span style=\"color: red;\">男</span>同學咀左啖 初吻咁就冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPS:勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2b6a8533b33e358515aaa34ccf30b9e6fbd59e7d","tid":357704,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T11:52:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小二同隔離位<span style=\"color: red;\">男</span>同學咀左啖 初吻咁就冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPS:勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n做乜無啦啦咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16adb47248b6bfca96a11f4b61c243dff34fe52b","tid":357704,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:18:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778676291a29179d2145e785fd1910e6d073da49","tid":357704,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:58:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e01d1c8489455ff810a6f8f5720bd8d57dea79","tid":357704,"uid":73349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"on9男同學訓左係我張櫈度我差啲坐左落去佢個頭度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb8eaad00c3cfe75553b8e3656c5e40b7f12462","tid":357704,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:02:32.000Z","msg":"有同學瀨屎又唔承 仲擺咗啲屎入櫃桶成個班房好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806e16f208c6b4ab285893221415188030344de5","tid":357704,"uid":4534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:18:11.000Z","msg":"有次上堂途中 個男同學舉手去廁所<br />\n去左好耐都未番黎<br />\n叫左個男仔去廁所搵佢<br />\n去到番黎 男仔細細聲同呀sir唔知講乜<br />\n然後走番去廁所 好快就番黎<br />\n<br />\n但本來舉手去廁所個個都係未番黎<br />\n所以咪問個男仔佢咩事<br />\n但佢仲好守秘密咩都唔撚講<br />\n<br />\n平時佢份人都好賤既<br />\n當我地以為佢咁正直咁有義氣既時候<br />\n點知條友都係忍唔住<br />\n一完左個堂 就爆出黎話：<br />\n「佢跑到去廁格 但都趕唔切 賴左屎<br />\n我入到去個時 已經見到佢拎住個地拖搞搞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢仲話比十蚊我叫我唔好同人講」<br />\n<br />\n笑到我地到宜家仲記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770fbffa42c206d0a90185dfb1986d013add8e5f","tid":357704,"uid":116320,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"小學五年級踢學界比賽 <br />\n隔離個後衛係同班同學 大陸仔嚟 平時都好刻人憎<br />\n踢踢吓唔知邊個傳波俾佢 點知佢踢嗰吓踩波車 <br />\n啪！ 一聲仆落地下<br />\n喊住爬返起身 成口血 斷晒兩隻門牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗返起都想笑"},{"pid":"179ef517c6c8143f45259870fce8e6d9ca7f2884","tid":357704,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T04:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9男同學訓左係我張櫈度我差啲坐左落去佢個頭度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢原本係想批個頭比你當櫈坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b69cb9081f90288e62e13b6ffd6b7ea48d99e71","tid":357704,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有同學瀨屎又唔承 仲擺咗啲屎入櫃桶成個班房好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n櫃桶心諗:dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}